{
    "type": "webhook",
    "name": "start_deep_trip_analysis",
    "description": "Use for broad Norway trip-planning questions that need whole-itinerary reasoning, slower compute, or a more capable async model. Examples include whether there is a better way to do the trip, next-five-days highlights, route improvement, variant comparison, weather-driven replanning, or substantial tradeoff analysis. Do not use for simple whole-trip must-see summaries that can be answered from route context. Returns an internal reference for follow-up; do not read it aloud.",
